price: Guyyaa Nuti jahannamiin “sila guutamteettaa?” jennuun, isheen immoo “dabalanni jiraa?” jettu (isaan sodaachidi.)
arabic: يَوۡمَ نَقُولُ لِجَهَنَّمَ هَلِ ٱمۡتَلَأۡتِ وَتَقُولُ هَلۡ مِن مَّزِيدٖ

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: yawma naqūlu lijahannama hali im'talati wataqūlu hal min mazīdin
